high_descs: Take a step right and walk ahead to the counter.
Pick up the mug on the counter.
Turn around and veer right to the fridge.
Place the mug in the fridge and close the door. Wait a moment, then take the mug out.
Turn around and veer right to the coffee maker in the corner near the sink.
Place the mug in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled mug in a coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the sink, then hang a left and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the white mug off of the counter.
Walk to the fridge that is across the room behind you.
Put the mug in the fridge for a couple seconds and let it get cold, then take it out and close the fridge.
Turn left and walk towards the sink, then hang a left and walk up to the oven, turn right and walk forward.
Put the chilled mug into the coffee machine on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug in the coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter to the right of the stove that's on your left and stand facing it.
Pick up the mug that's on the right side of the stove.
Turn around and walk to the fridge that's on your right and stand facing it.
Chill the mug in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the counter then turn left and walk to that counter then turn right.
Put the mug in it's spot at the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug under the coffee pot.
